                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4657" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0371</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9161 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从邯郸学步到择善而从——兰州海鸿的绩效考核之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Imitate Others Mechanically to Choose and Follow What is Right--Lanzhou Haihong Performance Appraisal Road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张璐，耿燕男，季柯辛（通讯作者），张强，长青，马鸿亮，肇先</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏敬勤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰州海鸿餐饮管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿米巴经营；绩效考核；激励；2020百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Amoeba operation; Performance appraisal; incentive</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰州海鸿餐饮管理有限公司（以下简称“海鸿”）作为西北地区的大众化餐饮龙头企业，在2018年前后遭遇了发展瓶颈。员工相互推诿扯皮和磨洋工等现象严重，原材料成本上升，行业竞争加剧。一系列“内忧外患”迫使董事长马鸿亮通过引入阿米巴模式进行绩效考核寻求突破，但过程并非一帆风顺，“强力推销”、“偷工减料”等忽视顾客感受的新问题相继出现。为了使阿米巴成功“落地”海鸿，马总带领员工设计出“四色卡”考核体系，同时加强“致良知”培训。一系列的努力终于有了成效，开创了企业经营管理的新局面。该案例旨在帮助学生理解掌握绩效考核的相关理论，为我国中小企业引进先进的绩效考核模式，并结合企业特点有效应用提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Lanzhou Haihong Catering Management Co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Haihong&quot;), as a leading enterprise of popular catering in northwest China, has also encountered development bottleneck around 2018.The phenomenon of employees bucking each other and loafing over work is serious, and the cost of raw materials is rising, and the competition in the industry is intensified. A series of &quot;internal and external troubles&quot; forced Chairman Ma Hongliang to seek breakthrough through the introduction of amoeba model performance assessment, but the process is not smooth, &quot;strong selling&quot;, &quot;cut cuts&quot; and a series of new problems ignore customer feelings have emerged. In order to successfully land amoeba in Haihong, Mr. Ma led the staff to design the &quot;four-color card&quot; assessment system and strengthen the &quot;conscience&quot; training. A series of efforts have finally yielded results and opened up a new situation of enterprise management. This case aims to help students understand and master relevant theories of performance appraisal, and provide reference for S&amp;M enterprises in China to introduce advanced performance appraisal mode and effectively apply it in combination with enterprise characteristics.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绩效管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
